        <li>(d) Tap News may receive personal data about Users from public sources (such as phone directories, advertising information/flyers, publicly available information on electronic news pages).</li>
    </ul>
</li>

<li>Whenever personal data is collected in this way, Tap News will ensure that receiving data from relevant third parties is done in legal ways, while requiring those third parties to comply with the legal provisions regarding the protection of personal data.</li>

